{"tid":2397050,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"蘇超後衛刷新C朗1紀錄，C朗專程要打電話為對方送上祝賀","createTime":"2021-02-06T06:12:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-06T08:04:45.000Z","uid":25345,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"085658b2144cbafcdfaf8f8a3b23bcc4d86f4f23","tid":2397050,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T06:12:47.000Z","msg":"眾所周知C羅的彈跳力在世界足壇數一數二，他更是創下了2米56起跳總高度，離地高度達到71公分。但是近日在蘇超羅斯郡與馬瑟韋爾的比賽當中，馬瑟韋爾的後衛貝維斯穆加比在比賽當中憑藉頭球攻入1球，這粒進球也讓他刷新了C羅的起跳高度紀錄。<br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0205%2F13b3ce32j00qo1toi0011c000hs00dlm.jpg&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0205%252F13b3ce32j00qo1toi0011c000hs00dlm.jpg%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=ad63606e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n  <br />\n<br />\n  根據烏克蘭媒體的報導，在蘇超這場比賽當中，貝維斯穆加比在第72分鐘的頭追破門刷新了一項新的紀錄，他的起跳總高度達到了2米62，離地高度達到了75公分，這樣的成績也刷新了此前由C羅保持的世界紀錄2米56，離地高度71公分的成績。<br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0205%2F2fcf4181j00qo1toi000mc000hs00bym.jpg&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0205%252F2fcf4181j00qo1toi000mc000hs00bym.jpg%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=b0704e01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n  <br />\n<br />\n  在C羅得知此消息後表現出了他的風度，總裁專門要到了貝維斯穆加比的電話，向他進行了電話祝賀，祝福他帶領球隊飛得更高，職業生涯也一定能刷新一個高度。相信這粒進球也讓穆加比十分驚喜，接到C羅的電話祝賀也必定會激勵他繼續前進。"},{"pid":"484c184c80fff6bf93ac669cb5d83a12e584204a","tid":2397050,"uid":286473,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T06:14:56.000Z","msg":"有d誇張"},{"pid":"7193ccb3f3c03362267b108553f15358dc8f1cd3","tid":2397050,"uid":307927,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTim